            "chunk_index": 1,
            "text": "113 OG No. 46, 8205 (November 13, 2017); Manila Bulletin, November 3, 2017\n\n[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 10956, October 30, 2017 ]\n\nAN ACT CREATING A BARANGAY TO BE KNOWN AS BARANGAY CARE IN THE CITY OF TARLAC, PROVINCE OF TARLAC\n\nBe it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:\n\nSECTION 1.\n\nCreation of Barangay Care.\n\n- There is hereby created a barangay to be known as Barangay care in the City of Tarlac, Province of Tarlac.",
            "metadata": {
                "law_id": "RA_10956",
                "date": "October 30, 2017"
            }
        },
        {
            "chunk_index": 2,
            "text": "SEC. 2.\n\nTerritorial Boundaries.\n\n- The territorial boundaries of Barangay Care shall be identified as follows:\n\nBounded on the Northeast (NE) and Southeast (SE), along lines 1 to 61, by Barangay Tibag (PB-03-000061);\n\nOn the Southeast (SE) and Southwest (SW), along lines 61 to 95, by Barangay Tibagan (PB-03-000061);\n\nOn the Southwest (SW) and the Northwest (NW), along lines 95 to 106, by Tarlac City versus Municipality of San Jose, both in Tarlac;\n\nOn the Northwest (NW), along lines 106 to 108, by San Jose Cadastre (PB-03-000060);\n\nOn the Northeast (NE), along lines 108 to 114, by Tarlac City versus Municipality of San Jose, Tarlac;\n\nOn the North (N) and West (W), along lines 114 to 116, by San Jose Cadastre (PB-03-000060);\n\nOn the Northeast (NE) and Northwest (NW), along lines 116 to 143 to the point of beginning by Barangay Sapang Maragul (PB-03-000061), all of Tarlac City.\n\nThe technical description of Barangay Care is as follows:\n\nTIEPOINT 1\n\nN\n\n78\n\n44\n\nW\n\n3,617.29\n\nBLLM # 1-A (PRS 92) (PB-03-000061), CAD 274, Tarlac Cadastre\n\nN.1712915.536 E. 455693.776\n\n1\n\n2\n\nN\n\n53\n\n31\n\nW\n\n15.76\n\n2\n\n3\n\nS\n\n35\n\n13\n\nE\n\n14.30\n\n3\n\n4\n\nS\n\n40\n\n49\n\nE\n\n212.14\n\n4\n\n5\n\nS\n\n37\n\n51\n\nE\n\n128.99\n\n5\n\n6\n\nS\n\n37",
